snippet.title: Johnny Depp Vs. Amber Heard The Complete Story part 2
snippet.description:
Description Box

Hello Friends! In this part two video we start from the end of the UK trial and get all caught up and updated with everything until the present. Now that we will all be completely caught up, whenever anything new breaks, I will be able to make a quick video to update everyone and we will all know exactly what is going on!
I want to show my support and thanks to That Umbrella Guy. He is a great YouTuber and covers this case extremely well.

Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard ""The Complete Story" part 1 - https://youtu.be/CMxp-tlyQrw
That  Umbrella Guys Channel - https://www.youtube.com/user/GranularHeaven
Video Explaining the conflict of interest with the Judge in the UK trial - 
Video 
The equipment I use: 
Camera - The video footage was shot using a Canon EOS M50 Mark 2
My microphone -  is a Blue Yeticaster professional broadcast bundle. With yeti USB microphone, Radius 3 shockmount, and Compass Boom Arm
The lighting - I use is a GVM bicolor LED video light
The video editing program - I use is Cyberlink Powerdirector 365 version 19

Please follow me on social media!
Instagram - Metalmomma5114
Twitter - @AnaniaChanda
Facebook - Metal Momma

Thank you all so much for watching this video! I appreciare it so much! Please share all your thoughts with me, I love hearing everything you all have to say! Thank you so much!
